arStrings.szText: {c_important}Trample{/c} now summons {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} {c_important}Landslide{/c} pillars of earth during its duration that deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} normal damage. {c_important}Trample{/c} is now also a {c_important}Nature Magic{/c} and {c_important}Earth{/c} Skill.
